Package: orchideecore
Title: Portable Core for the ORCHIDEE RATB Indicator Catalogue
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("ORCHIDEE", "Maintainers", email = "orchidee@example.invalid", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the complete auditable ORCHIDEE RATB indicator
    catalogue from a validated canonical bundle through plausibility quality
    control, global and by-type patient-year deduplication, isolate-level
    indicator results, annual resistance proportions, and annual incidence.
    Completion, reporting, caching, and hospital-specific extraction are
    excluded.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
